{"title": "Heart of Happy Hollow", "description": "Happy Hollow; are you wondering where it is? Wherever Negroes colonise in the cities or villages, north or south, wherever the hod carrier, the porter, and the waiter are the society men of the town; wherever the picnic and the excursion are the chief summer diversion, and the revival the winter time of repentance, wherever the cheese cloth veil obtains at a wedding, and the little white hearse goes by with black mourners in the one carriage behind, there\u2014there\u2014is Happy Hollow. Wherever laughter and tears rub elbows day by day, and the spirit of labour and laziness shake hands, there\u2014there\u2014is Happy Hollow, and of some of it may the following pages show the heart. (Summary by the author)", "duration": 15392, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "546", "name": "Paul Laurence Dunbar"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/heart_of_happy_hollow_2209_librivox/heart_happy_hollow_2209.jpg", "copyright_year": "1904", "genres": ["Culture & Heritage Fiction", "Short Stories"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Jim Locke"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Jim Locke"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "DaveC"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "DaveC"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "The Scapegoat", "readers": [10801], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_of_happy_hollow_2209_librivox/heartofhappyhollow_01_dunbar_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1539}, {"section": 2, "title": "One Christmas at Shiloh", "readers": [10801], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_of_happy_hollow_2209_librivox/heartofhappyhollow_02_dunbar_64kb.mp3", "duration": 977}, {"section": 3, "title": "The Mission of Mr. Scatters", "readers": [10801], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_of_happy_hollow_2209_librivox/heartofhappyhollow_03_dunbar_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1797}, {"section": 4, "title": "A Matter of Doctrine", "readers": [10801], "path": "https://www.archive.org/down